General.Name: Netum Group Oyj
General.Description: Netum Group Oyj operates as an IT services company in Finland. The company offers digital service development, system continuity, data and analysis, integration, and cyber security services as well as management consulting services. It also provides Netum Dux, a system for IT asset management; and Truugo, an advanced testing and documentation platform for structured data. The company serves public administration and corporate customers. Netum Group Oyj was founded in 2000 and is based in Tampere, Finland.
